:- pred terms_sort(+Asub,-Asub_s): absu * absu
# 
"It sorts the set of @var{X}:@var{Type} in @var{Asub} ontaining @var{Asub_s}".

terms_sort('$bottom','$bottom'):- !.
terms_sort(ASub,ASub_s):- sort(ASub,ASub_s).

