:- pred terms_call_to_success_fact(+Sg,+Hv,+Head,+Sv,+Call,+Proj,-Prime,-Succ): callable * 
list * callable * list * absu * absu * absu * absu # 
"Specialized version of call_to_entry + exit_to_prime + extend for facts".

terms_call_to_success_fact(Sg,Hv,Head,Sv,Call,Proj,Prime,Succ):-
	terms_call_to_entry(Sg,Hv,Head,[],Proj,Entry,ExtraInfo),
	terms_exit_to_prime(Sg,Hv,Head,Sv,Entry,ExtraInfo,Prime),
	terms_extend(Prime,Sv,Call,Succ).




